ed="T" n="0886c01"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0886c01"/><head><date from-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322132856" to-iso="+1127-06-18"><anchor xml:id="begd1e48941"/>宋<anchor xml:id="endd1e48941"/></date><placeName key="PL000000023417">東京普淨院</placeName><persName key="A010320">常覺</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0886c02"/><persName key="A010320">釋常覺</persName>，姓<name>李氏</name>，<placeName key="PL000000023329">陳留</placeName>人也。肇為鞠子<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2311"/>，氣調<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2312"/><lb
ed="T" n="0886c03"/>絕奇，入鄉校中諷讀經籍，群童咸出其下。<lb
ed="T" n="0886c04"/>洎登弱冠，往<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬山</placeName>遊<placeName key="PLG00000000014">二林</placeName>，陟<placeName key="PL000000018780">五老</placeName>，乃<anchor xml:id="beg0886sgsz7"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0886sgsz7"/><lb
ed="T" n="0886c05"/><placeName key="PL000000018960">歸宗寺</placeName><ref type="person" target="#A019511">禪師</ref><ptr target="#n3470"/>，充苦行焉！<date from-iso="+0912-01-27" key="j20541872054570" to-iso="+0913-02-13"><name>梁</name><name>乾化</name>二年</date>，蒙去<lb
ed="T" n="0886c06"/>飾披緇矣。<ref type="date" target="#j20545712054924">明年</ref>，於<placeName key="PL000000018804"><placeName>東林</placeName><placeName>甘露戒壇</placeName></placeName>納解脫<lb
ed="T" n="0886c07"/>木叉<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1202"/>。厥後修身踐言，雖三藏俱留於意表<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2313"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0886c08"/>而以心學<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2314"/>為究盡之務。復入<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0886sgsz11"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0886sgsz11"/><persName key="A002144">妙<lb
ed="T" n="0886c09"/>吉</persName>靈跡。迨<date from-iso="+0928-01-31" key="j20600352060418" to-iso="+0929-02-17"><name>後唐</name><name>天成</name>三載</date>，始於<placeName key="PL000000023406"><placeName>東京</placeName><placeName>麗景<lb
ed="T" n="0886c10"/>門</placeName></placeName>之右樹小禪坊，勅額為<placeName key="PL000000023417">普淨</placeName>焉<ptr target="#n3471"/>！而逐月<lb
ed="T" n="0886c11"/>三八日設闔京僧浴。其或香湯汲注，樵蒸<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2315"/>失<lb
ed="T" n="0886c12"/>供，<persName key="A010320">覺</persName>必令撤小屋，抽榱桷<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2316"/>而助爨焉！有公<lb
ed="T" n="0886c13"/>王仰重，表<anchor xml:id="beg0886sgsz13"/>薦<anchor xml:id="end0886sgsz13"/>紫衣，堅拒弗受<ptr target="#n3472"/>，汲汲以利行<lb
ed="T" n="0886c14"/>濟物為<anchor xml:id="beg0886sgsz15"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0886sgsz15"/>任耳！<date key="j20760722076072" when-iso="+0971-12-28"><name>開寶</name>四年十二月三日</date><ptr target="#n3473"/>遘<lb
ed="T" n="0886c15"/>疾，輕安無撓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2317"/>。<date key="j20760802076080" when-iso="+0972-01-05">十一日</date>告眾，右脇而化。享年<lb
ed="T" n="0886c16"/>七十六，僧臘五十六。茶毘收舍利，五色磊<lb
ed="T" n="0886c17"/>落無算。甞居<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023467">京邑</ref>，屢登<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023417">斯院</ref>，覽<placeName key="PL000000021024">北海</placeName><persName key="A011980">陶<roleName>尚<lb
ed="T" n="0886c18"/>書</roleName>穀</persName>《為<placeName key="PL000000028911">湘東</placeName><persName key="A013805">張仲荀</persName>序詩贈<persName key="A010320">覺</persName>》<ptr target="#n3476"/>而云：「起<date notBefore-iso="+0926-06-16" key="j20594412068464" notAfter-iso="+0951-02-28"><name>後<lb
ed="T" n="0886c19"/>唐</name><name>天成</name>至<name>漢</name><name>乾祐</name></date>，每黑白月三取八日<ptr target="#n3474"/>，浴<lb
ed="T" n="0886c20"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000023467">京</ref>大眾，累歲費錢可一百三十六萬數，計緡<lb
ed="T" n="0886c21"/>千萬矣。雖檀施<ptr type="glossary" target="#g237"/>共成，實<persName key="A010320">覺<roleName>公</roleName></persName>化導之力也。嘻！<lb
ed="T" n="0886c22"/><name>大火</name>之下，<placeName key="PL000000023329">陳留</placeName>古封<ptr target="#n3475"/>，<placeName key="PL000000042030">周</placeName><placeName key="PL000000000096">秦</placeName>已來，戰伐之國，人<lb
ed="T" n="0886c23"/>物眾而土風尚利，舟車會而貨殖惟錯<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2318"/>。昔<persName key="A013806">梁<lb
ed="T" n="0886c24"/>惠王</persName>賢諸侯也，甞謂<persName key="A004486">孟軻</persName>曰：『何以利<ref type="person" target="#A013806">吾</ref>國？<ptr target="#n3477"/>』<lb
ed="T" n="0886c25"/>是知禮讓之化，不勝於好利之心，明矣！且<placeName key="PL000000023338">梁</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0886c26"/>去<placeName key="PL000000021513">魯</placeName>千里而近，道猶不同，矧<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g325"/>十萬八千里<lb
ed="T" n="0886c27"/>乎？<persName key="A013806">梁王</persName>、<persName key="A004486">孟子</persName>，同世之人也，心或有異，況<persName key="A010320">瞿曇<lb
ed="T" n="0886c28"/>上人</persName>乎？彼<persName key="A004486">孟氏</persName>屬斯文<ptr target="#n3478"/>未喪，不能揚<persName key="A002174">素王</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0886c29"/>之道；<ref type="person" target="#A010320">今上人</ref>當去聖逾遠，卒能行<persName key="A002799">法王</persName>之<pb ed="T" n="0887a" xml:id="T50.2061.0887a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0887a01"/>教，苟非三業<ptr type="glossary" target="#g29"/>內淨，六塵<ptr type="glossary" target="#g384"/>外清，以至公之行<lb
ed="T" n="0887a02"/>化於人，孰以至公之心受於化也！」<persName key="A011980">陶</persName>重敘<lb
ed="T" n="0887a03"/>曰：「自<placeName key="PL000000048268">靈山</placeName>覆簣，法海<anchor xml:id="beg0887001"/>堙<anchor xml:id="end0887001"/>流，玉毫晦而微言<lb
ed="T" n="0887a04"/>絕<ptr target="#n3479"/>，金杖折<ptr target="#n3480"/>而異端作。惟<ref type="person" target="#A010320">上人</ref>也色空等觀，物<lb
ed="T" n="0887a05"/>我都亡。麻麥一齋，自同禪悅<ptr target="#n3481"/>；炎涼一納，僅蔽<lb
ed="T" n="0887a06"/>枯形。前後王臣欲上章乞以大師為號，請<lb
ed="T" n="0887a07"/>以紫染方袍者，皆確而拒之」云云。<persName key="A013805">張仲荀</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0887a08"/>贈<persName key="A010320">覺</persName>鉢盂拄杖草屨，各用五言為章，刊于<lb
ed="T" n="0887a09"/>小碣。其為名流碩學，旌別有如此者。</p>
